<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<em><strong>No spoilers here, please. <p>
NO SPOILERS HERE!</em></strong> 
</p>
<p>
A Summoner is, with one exception, a fairly weak class. While he starts  out a decent enough fighter, his fighting skill doesn't improve that much, he doesn't cast magic and he has little in the way of survival skills. However, this weakness doesn't trouble him much, because he can summon creatures to do his bidding and still gain experience from their kills. 
</p>
<p>
Starting stat modifiers, starting Skills, innate abilities and starting equipment: Please see the in-game help. 
</p>
